/camera	: camera model, projection and rectification
/database	: database of sequences for off-line demo
/fast		: fast feature detector and tracker
/framework	: main framework of the project
/geom		: basic geometric objects (vertices, edges, faces, etc.)
/include	: basic includes (colors)
/ladybug	: code for interacting with the Ladybug
/lib		: libraries
/math		: basic math
/model	: 3D model operations
/scripts	: a few scripts for Ladybug images management
/sfm		: SFM code (inactive)
/signature	: Lookup Table for visibility precomputation
/timer	: performance timer
/util		: a bunch of useful functions
/viewer	: generic openGL viewer
/viscomp	: standalone application for visibility precomputation



